This thing on the side that I'm toggling over here, this is our Snowflake VS Code extension.

00:11:49.239 --> 00:11:54.640
So you kind of get that for free with Positron, because we designed it to work with VS Code.

00:11:54.640 --> 00:11:56.400
Now with Positron, you get that for free.

00:11:56.400 --> 00:12:00.280
That lets us kind of peek in here to what's going on inside my Snowflake account.

